Content.bodyText:
Darren - this looks great! I can't wait to try it out. 

Last night I was on a webinar about SEO where the speaker was saying that Wordpress was the best CMS for SEO - partly because of an auto-linking plugin, and I thought, I bet umbraco can do that too. 

Thanks for proving me right :-)

~Heather
